CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, page A11, reads: "Attractive Visitors... always help to glamorize the Frog Week. This trio was at the closed party for members and out-of-town guests at Loendi Sunday. Left to right: Mrs. Walter Cole, Harrisburg, Pa.; Mrs. Mary (Betty) Lee Brady, Chicago, Ill; Miss Doris Freeland, Baltimore. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mrs. Walter Cole, Mary "Betty" Lee Brady, and Doris Freeland, gathered on Loendi Club porch for FROGS week event, horizontal format
